# Component Rules

## General
- All components are functional with TypeScript props interface
- Use shadcn/ui for form elements (Input, Button, Checkbox, Select)
- Use Framer Motion for animations (motion.div, AnimatePresence)
- Tailwind for all styling, no CSS modules or styled-components

## SeatMap Component
- 10 rows × 4 seats (A, B | aisle | C, D)
- SVG or div grid layout — choose simpler option
- States: free (gray), occupied (dark + icon), selected (gold glow)
- Occupied seats are NOT clickable
- On click: Framer Motion animation → navigate to /vyhra with prize data
- Fetch seat occupancy status from /api/seats on mount
- Show loading skeleton while fetching

## RegistrationForm Component
- Client component ('use client')
- Use react-hook-form or native form with useState
- Inline validation with Czech error messages
- Fields: jméno, příjmení, email, telefon, datum narození, soutěžní otázka, 2× checkbox
- Phone: accept +420 format, validate pattern
- Date: must be 18+ (calculate from today)
- On submit: POST to /api/register, show success/error state
- Disable submit button during loading

## PrizeReveal Component
- Full-screen modal or new page (/vyhra)
- Framer Motion entrance animation
- Prize type determines: icon, color, text, animation intensity
- Main prize (trip): gold + confetti effect
- Other prizes: matching color animation
- CTA after reveal: "Sdílet" or "Zpět na hlavní stránku"

## HeroSection Component
- Full viewport height on desktop, auto on mobile
- Light background (#E8ECF0) with decorative cloud/mountain SVG elements
- Hero plane image prominently displayed (not as dark overlay background)
- Centered claim text (dark #1A1A2E) + red CTA button (#C8102E)
- Smooth scroll to registration form on CTA click
- Logo bar below or overlaid
- Overall feel: clean, illustrative, airy — like a travel poster

